item.title: Nigeria Automotive Market Analysis for Tsuyomi Motors
item.description: 1.0 Introduction Tsuyoi Motors (強い車) is an international car-dealing organisation seeking to break into the Nigerian automotive market with a focus on recently manufactured cars. However, they are faced with multifaceted problems.
